      "step_order_index": 13,
      "assistant_prompt": "üéâ **Thank you!**\n\nYour feedback is incredibly valuable. We'll analyze all responses and use them to build something that actually solves your problem.\n\nWant to stay in the loop? We'll email you when we have updates.\n\nThanks for your time! üôè",
